data.label: after
data.description: material after the end of the word

data.label: appositioncontainer
data.description: 1 if it is an apposition container

data.label: articular
data.description: 1 if the sentence, group, clause, phrase or wg has an article

data.label: bookshort
data.description: book name (abbreviated) from ref attribute in xml

data.label: chapter
data.description: chapter number, from ref attribute in xml

data.label: discontinuous
data.description: 1 if the word is out of sequence in the xml

data.label: nodeid
data.description: node id (as in the XML source data)

data.label: num
data.description: generated number (not in xml): book: (Matthew=1, Mark=2, ..., Revelation=27); sentence: numbered per chapter; word: numbered per verse.

data.label: trailer
data.description: material after the end of the word (excluding critical signs)

data.label: trans
data.description: translation of the word surface text according to the Berean Interlinear Bible

data.label: translit
data.description: transliteration of the word surface text

data.label: typ
data.description: syntactical type (on sentence, group, clause or phrase)

data.label: typems
data.description: morphological type (on word), syntactical type (on sentence, group, clause, phrase or wg)

data.label: unaccent
data.description: word in unicode characters without accents and diacritical markers

data.label: unicode
data.description: word in unicode characters plus material after it

data.label: verse
data.description: verse number, from ref attribute in xml
